The '''Wishing Lake '''was an area of space located near the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]]. It was first named by deep-space [[Mercenary/Legends|mercenaries]] employed by the [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation]]. It was void of activity and passing through the area was said to be a bad omen.

